      • setWeatherDuration

        public static void setWeatherDuration(org.bukkit.World world,
                                      int durationInTicks)
        Sets the weather duration of the current weather state, until it switches to a future state. To make the current weather state last forever, specify a duration of Integer.MAX_VALUE.

        The future weather state will always go from clear <> rain/storm.

        world - to set the weather duration for
